{"tid":939261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一地兩檢覆核】高院裁定安排符合《基本法》市民挑戰失敗","createTime":"2018-12-13T03:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T06:15:52.000Z","uid":54870,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"11d0a646f43e18a0e0851592056f089666858e83","tid":939261,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:19:57.000Z","msg":"立法會今年6月通過高鐵「一地兩檢」安排並刊憲，接連有多名市民提請司法覆核。案件在高鐵通車約一個月後審理，法官周家明今早頒下判詞，認為一地兩檢符合《基本法》，裁定市民敗訴。<br />\n<br />\n申請人分別為青年新政召集人梁頌恆、社民連成員梁國雄、「長洲覆核王」郭卓堅及社工呂智恆。申請人一方審訊時形容，一地兩檢相當於「在香港特區之內創造一個小特區」，人大常委會批准安排，恍如一揮魔杖變出「綠洲」，在西九總站內地口岸區取消實施本港法律，全面改行內地法律，猶如「放入怪物」，變成一國一制，違反載於《中英聯合聲明》和《基本法》的中央對港基本方針。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181213/59024467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181213%2F59024467&d=jlMUGUNBB2JG8BQortsepb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=1690e5ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181213%2F59024467&h=25a3609c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181213/59024467</a>"},{"pid":"def2138875a05a045e4cbe3b4f7ac1e7ad46cc59","tid":939261,"uid":3117,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:20:48.000Z","msg":"港共連法院都控制晒"},{"pid":"e3f3de9d59f14d0fb57a1dce16d7e873c30422a2","tid":939261,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d14441daba159f96c4212aea4ad00f358df0aab","tid":939261,"uid":77196,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:29:49.000Z","msg":"法官周家明今早頒下判詞，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">認為一地兩檢符合《基本法》</span></strong>，裁定市民敗訴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未審先判 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a9dacf8dab87c3c4d81a3946a8e90c7e6c